{"tid":775841,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"唔識溝通仲有冇去旅行既意義？","createTime":"2018-08-11T13:24:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-12T10:34:36.000Z","uid":37726,"like":4,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"cad2d989d5c1998a52c0145835475647a92ee433","tid":775841,"uid":37726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T13:24:58.000Z","msg":"出遊次數唔多 成日都想周圍去<br />\n但係因為唔識當地嘅語言 唔夠膽獨遊 <br />\n就算同朋友去 同行既都未必識<br />\n最多都係勉強用英文<br />\n<br />\n好似去個日本 唔識講日文<br />\n連嗌野食都有難度<br />\n唉 我都係認認真真學啲語言旁下身<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申 只識廣東話"},{"pid":"ef6860a087744bc1625f31be50bd2e69ad733c2c","tid":775841,"uid":198583,"like":2,"dislike":15,"score":-13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T13:26:09.000Z","msg":"It is pathetic that you cant even speak in English when you are abroad<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6eb4e61a7c8b488bd205b627e9a625208cdbe9c8","tid":775841,"uid":31173,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T13:26:23.000Z","msg":"咁咪學囉？做乜鳩？"},{"pid":"526344c589fbc1dc9fbd422cf84bb4aaebd688a5","tid":775841,"uid":72240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T13:27:51.000Z","msg":"怕咩"},{"pid":"d5c7a5a4df55ac0b029c89278bd362a0743a1c33","tid":775841,"uid":120715,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T13:29:27.000Z","msg":"我試過一個人去日本 仲要第一次去<br />\n我唔識日文, 英文都麻麻<br />\n但第一日反而有個德國佬同我吹水<br />\n之後亦都有日同幾個日本妹吹過下水<br />\n大家都係英文麻麻地<br />\n但都識到下當地人<br />\n叫野食都係點圖<br />\n同埋日本餐牌好多都有中文版"},{"pid":"7b6c0753e355d82f830de5f7016af206379f12be","tid":775841,"uid":194894,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T13:30:15.000Z","msg":"估唔到仲有後生仔咁諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ada220cda147c262f2b446288b4ae31b80d9ae4","tid":775841,"uid":1